    "Here, we are interested in the ways in which people can detect the authorship of texts that people present as justifications for their answers and as data quality checks.",
    "This leads to our next research questions: RQ4: How accurately can participants identify the authors of the stimuli?",
    "RQ5: How accurate and reliable are automatic AI detection systems?",
    "RQ6: What is the relationship between the accuracy of AI detection systems and the accuracy of human participants?",
    "Interestingly, scholars have attempted to discern the criteria that participants use to make their decisions (Guo et al., 2023; Hämäläinen et al., 2023)."
